vice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟从5.5ms增加到300ms，倍数54倍\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "log_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的日志数据，我现在分析adservice-0的根因假设是否成立。以下是分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Agent failed to start\", \"Byteman agent\", \"java.lang.Exception\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Transformer\", \"Rule.execute\", \"AdService-getRandomAds-latency\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent启动失败导致严重性能问题 - Agent failed to start和Byteman agent重复加载异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Agent failed to start! Caused by: java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once, Rule.execute called for AdService-getRandomAds-latency-1749575407_29:0 (出现1373次)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析依据：**\n\n1. **关键错误模式识别**：\n   - 明确的Byteman agent启动失败：`Agent failed to start!`\n   - Byteman agent重复加载异常：`attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`\n   - 大量的规则执行日志：`Rule.execute`调用出现1373次，表明性能监控规则被频繁触发\n\n2. **证据链支持假设**：\n   - 所有错误日志都来自adservice-0服务\n   - Byteman agent启动失败直接解释了为什么adservice会出现严重的性能退化（rrt从3.4ms增加到127.9ms）\n   - 大量的`Rule.execute`调用表明系统在异常状态下持续尝试执行性能监控规则，进一步加剧了性能问题\n\n3. **与Metric和Trace数据的关联**：\n   - 日志中的性能监控规则（`AdService-getRandomAds-latency`）与Metric专家观察到的rrt指标飙升完全一致\n   - Byteman agent故障导致的服务性能下降解释了Trace专家观察到的frontend服务连锁延迟问题\n\n因此，日志数据强烈支持\"adservice-0 is the root cause due to severe performance degradation and Byteman agent startup failures\"这一假设。"}
